name: Instant-lyrics
tagline: look up lyrics for the currently playing song
body:
Have lyrics you want on your screen in the blink of an eye. 
 - Triggers google search based on what is currently playing
 - Works with stock music app
 - Quickly open in safari


Open up music app, play a song, and let Instant Lyrics find lyrics for you!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
